com.brashmonkey.spriter

Class Curve

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.brashmonkey.spriter.Curve

  • public class Curve
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a curve in a Spriter SCML file. An instance of this class is responsible for tweening given data. The most important method of this class is tween(float, float, float). Curves can be changed with sub curves subCurve.
